{"tid":1749194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和你排 冇得投票手足請入","createTime":"2019-11-24T02:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T03:15:41.000Z","uid":307735,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"173bc24fa62de726040719b01121a0195270c31e","tid":1749194,"uid":307735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"for唔夠18既手足 適合任何人做<br />\n係票站外瘋狂隊 <br />\n有啲廢老 見到咁多人 做個勢出黎 佢地會懶得投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相廢老投既票少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好做到任何時段都咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4817edcf6fed02663be6913be49fdbd61ac11d","tid":1749194,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:26:37.000Z","msg":"排隊師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bbd0528765b25a5a2323af6006c82129124c3b","tid":1749194,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fee925589e2e5e5f69375d96a7f12a1a5f5b42ad","tid":1749194,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bb0ed21a3485edbd3b51497f560912f1a0ff9b","tid":1749194,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"diu...好能多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f377036b85a96edc4f288370acec913984ad11","tid":1749194,"uid":169040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"我反對<br />\n1）廢老時間多<br />\n佢哋未必介意排<br />\n反而趕走中間游離票<br />\n2）廢時有藉口話搗亂<br />\n今日我哋要製造一個和理非港豬出場嘅環境"},{"pid":"4ff3ecc609beb0033ec4ec977be2b16dac199ac6","tid":1749194,"uid":281516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"佢地一車一車咁去<br />\n搞手一定會等齊人先走<br />\n所以咁做只